{
  "id": "adv_event_2111_01_01",
  "title": "家族の存在",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅっ、今日のレッスンはここまでにしましょう\n二人とも、だいぶ息が上がってきてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ let’s end today’s lesson there.\nYou’re both out of breath.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1,
      "endTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～っ、助かった～！\n怜ちゃんとのレッスンはいつもハードだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* That’s a relief!\nLessons with you are always tough‚ Rei-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "endTime": 17.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ぜえぜえ、め、芽衣は、練習不足ですわね……\nこの程度のれ、れ、レッスンで音を上げるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*wheeze* Y-you’re out of practice‚ Mei.\nComplaining already in s-such an easy lesson…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.133333333333333,
      "endTime": 30.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　すずはまだまだ元気なのね\nじゃあ練習メニューを見直さないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? So you still have plenty of energy‚ Suzu?\nWell then‚ looks like I’ll have to review the lesson menu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665,
      "endTime": 38.06666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃー！　ごめんなさい、私、見栄を張りました！\n怜のダンスレッスンは、スパルタ過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eek! Sorry‚ I was just trying to show off!\nYour dance lessons are too extreme for me‚ Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 47.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、怜ちゃんは凄いよね\n芽衣も足がくがくだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Rei-chan‚ you’re awesome.\nMy legs are all wobbly too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1,
      "endTime": 54.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言いつつ、芽衣はまだ余裕がありそうですわね……\n私から見たら、二人とも体力おばけですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ Mei‚ but it looks like you still have some in the tank…\nFrom where I’m standing‚ you both look like muscle monsters…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55,
      "endTime": 65.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり怜ちゃんは、基礎体力が芽衣達とは違うよ\nダンス大会で優勝したことあるんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I figure that your physical fitness is on a totally different level from ours‚ Rei-chan.\nYou’ve won at dance tournaments‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7666666667,
      "endTime": 74.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……あんなの大したことないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kind of thing is no big deal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 76.5933333714803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "その謙遜した態度がかえって怜を凄く見せますわ\n私もそんな風に言ってみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That humble attitude just makes you look more awesome‚ Rei.\nI’d like to try talking like that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8,
      "endTime": 84.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "謙遜じゃないわ。本当に、あんなの意味がなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not being humble. Really‚ it didn’t mean anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 89.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？\nお父さんとかお母さん、喜んでくれなかったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why ever not?\nWeren’t your parents happy about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 94.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "二人には話してなかったっけ……全然よ。だから私は\nもっと大きな舞台を求めて、アイドルになったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have I never told you two about it? They showed no reaction.\nThat’s why I went looking for a much bigger stage‚ and became an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7333333333,
      "endTime": 104.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でもいまだに認めてもらえてない\n特に父とは冷戦状態よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they still don’t acknowledge me.\nIn particular‚ it’s like a cold war with my father.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2,
      "endTime": 111.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え！　NEXT VENUSグランプリで優勝したのに\n認めてもらえないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You won the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nand they still won’t acknowledge you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.46666666666667,
      "endTime": 116.93333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。そもそも芸能活動自体、よく思ってないみたい\nきっと軽薄な仕事だと思ってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It looks like they just don’t like the idea of how show business works.\nI’m sure they think it’s just a frivolous job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 125.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の家族は応援してくれてるから\nみんなも同じだと思ってたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei's family supports Mei‚\nso I thought everybody was the same…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 131.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "私は縁を切られているようなものよ\nたまに母から連絡が来るくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like they’ve disowned me.\nMy mother gets in touch sometimes‚ but that’s all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 138.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルはみんなを元気にする素敵なお仕事ですわ\n決して軽薄なんかじゃありませんのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being an idol is a wonderful job that cheers everyone up.\nIt’s certainly not “frivolous”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.76666666666668,
      "endTime": 146.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないわ、頭が固い人だから\n――あっ、はい。お疲れ様です、えっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can’t be helped‚ they’re stubborn.\n――Ah‚ yes. Thank you. Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 156,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33333333332007
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "新ユニット……？\nええ、私は構いませんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new team…?\nOkay‚ I don’t mind…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2,
      "endTime": 161.23333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。私から話します\n詳細はまた後で。失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ll talk to her.\nLet's go through the details later. Goodbye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4,
      "endTime": 167.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.666666666646
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、今の{user}さんだよね？\nなんの話？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan‚ that was {user}-san‚ right?\nWhat were you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 174.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "新ユニットって聞こえましたわ！\n大きな仕事のお話ですわね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you say “new team”!\nYou were talking about a big job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.9,
      "endTime": 179.69999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "期間限定で、新ユニットをやらないかって\nメンバーは、私と芽衣の二人らしいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He asked if I’d work as a new team for a limited period.\nApparently the two members are me and Mei…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.9,
      "endTime": 187.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！\nどうして私がメンバーに入っていないんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ wait a minute!\nWhy don’t I get to be a member?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.1333333333,
      "endTime": 192.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "それは{user}さんに言ってよ……\nダンスを売りにした混合ユニットらしいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should ask {user}-san about that.\nIt seems to be a new group with dancing as its selling point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.66666666666666,
      "endTime": 198.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2111_01_01-suz008.m4a",
